    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This beauty has been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed, and kept in pristine shape inside and out. It literally looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved to perfection, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
